WEBVTT

01:40.490 --> 01:45.910
[Speed and Love]

01:46.170 --> 01:48.770
[Episode 13]

01:50.070 --> 01:51.070
My hands are cold.

02:19.010 --> 02:23.610
[Yearning Day and Night]

02:28.320 --> 02:29.110
Does Jin Zhao

02:29.760 --> 02:30.920
have a girlfriend?

02:31.710 --> 02:33.640
I think the answer to your question

02:35.320 --> 02:36.780
is right on that ornament.

02:37.590 --> 02:40.190
It should be attached
to a certain key, I think.

02:40.200 --> 02:41.320
If you have time,

02:42.060 --> 02:43.060
you can go find it,

02:43.200 --> 02:45.000
and then you'll know the answer.

03:07.870 --> 03:10.200
Here! The freshly cut meat is ready.

03:12.800 --> 03:13.730
I'm warning you.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.920
Don't look at me with such adoring eyes.

03:15.920 --> 03:17.520
I've been single for so long
that even Xishi at the door

03:17.520 --> 03:19.110
looks pretty to me.

03:19.200 --> 03:20.270
What's making you so happy?

03:20.270 --> 03:23.150
Sanlai, you're such a good man.

03:24.870 --> 03:26.660
Well, what's going on?

03:27.270 --> 03:28.930
Have you really fallen for me?

03:31.920 --> 03:33.650
Stop being so full of yourself.

03:34.730 --> 03:36.060
Come on, take a big bite.

03:38.990 --> 03:41.240
I thought you didn't like
fennel dumplings.

03:41.240 --> 03:42.240
I don't know,

03:42.390 --> 03:44.300
but today's filling

03:44.320 --> 03:45.720
tastes especially good.

03:46.150 --> 03:48.079
You must be hungry
after getting caught in the rain.

03:48.079 --> 03:48.800
Here,

03:49.270 --> 03:51.480
let me get you a meatball.

03:52.650 --> 03:52.980
Here.

03:53.000 --> 03:53.920
Sanlai.

03:54.670 --> 03:56.600
I want one that Jin Zhao gets for me.

04:00.040 --> 04:01.960
Is my meatball poisoned or something?

04:01.960 --> 04:03.560
Fine, I won't get it. Come on.

04:15.760 --> 04:16.839
Mu, have a drink.

04:17.910 --> 04:18.680
Crazy.

04:19.390 --> 04:20.709
Are you really crazy?

04:21.230 --> 04:22.029
Brandy is here,

04:22.029 --> 04:23.360
and you persuaded Jiang Mu into drinking?

04:23.360 --> 04:26.160
-Exactly.
-Just drink the whole bottle yourself.

04:26.930 --> 04:27.830
Have one drink with me.

04:27.830 --> 04:28.710
-Sure.
-Drink with me.

04:28.710 --> 04:29.910
I'll finish mine.
You guys help yourselves.

04:29.910 --> 04:30.860
Let's drink then. Come on.

04:30.860 --> 04:32.520
Jiang Mu,
would you like something to drink?

04:32.520 --> 04:33.320
Soda, please.

04:33.590 --> 04:34.640
Do you want ice?

04:36.590 --> 04:38.710
Okay, any other requests?

04:39.710 --> 04:41.740
I want Jin Zhao to get my drink.

04:41.980 --> 04:42.500
Alright.

04:42.500 --> 04:44.030
-Come on, cheers.
-Come on.

04:44.840 --> 04:46.030
So I'm drinking alone?

04:46.030 --> 04:46.760
What a waste.

04:46.960 --> 04:48.020
Alright, alright.

05:09.080 --> 05:10.230
Brandy,

05:10.550 --> 05:12.310
I want a cold drink too!

05:23.640 --> 05:25.000
I've looked into

05:25.000 --> 05:26.200
the Scramble for you.

05:26.470 --> 05:28.800
It was the fruit farmers nearby
who did it.

05:29.470 --> 05:31.470
They sprinkled water on the track.

05:32.560 --> 05:34.890
They said they took money from Wan Dayong.

05:41.150 --> 05:41.880
It's okay.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.820
She knows everything.

05:45.230 --> 05:46.880
In the previous Scramble,

05:48.080 --> 05:49.470
she was my navigator.

05:51.150 --> 05:52.150
Navigator?

05:53.440 --> 05:54.200
Mu,

05:54.710 --> 05:56.390
do you know what a navigator

05:56.760 --> 05:58.520
means to a driver?

05:59.390 --> 06:00.470
It's like a lover.

06:01.270 --> 06:02.830
She can make a driver successful

06:02.830 --> 06:04.350
or get a driver killed.

06:05.440 --> 06:06.230
Brandy used to

06:06.230 --> 06:08.270
never trust anyone easily.

06:11.520 --> 06:12.830
Come on, join the table.

06:12.830 --> 06:15.090
You're holding us up. Shuffle the tiles.

07:23.080 --> 07:24.590
I'm done. I played the Red Dragon.

07:24.590 --> 07:25.390
Red Dragon.

07:26.270 --> 07:27.390
Eight of Characters.

07:27.390 --> 07:28.960
Kong it! Kong it!

07:31.270 --> 07:33.560
-What kind of play is that?
-I knew it.

07:34.520 --> 07:37.150
-And you played the Two of Bamboos.
-Kong the Two of Bamboos.

07:37.150 --> 07:38.420
Two of Bamboos. Your turn.

07:38.420 --> 07:39.740
Brandy, hurry up.

07:39.760 --> 07:40.440
Let me have one.

07:40.440 --> 07:42.390
-One tile away.
- One of Bamboos.

07:42.790 --> 07:44.790
-One of Bamboos. No One of Bamboos.
-Four of Characters.

07:44.790 --> 07:45.970
No Four of Characters.

07:45.970 --> 07:47.230
I just need one more tile to win.

07:47.230 --> 07:49.350
-Why are you holding my tile?
-Five of Circles.

07:49.350 --> 07:50.280
Five of Circles.

07:51.440 --> 07:52.480
That's the Five of Bamboos.

07:52.480 --> 07:53.150
-Five of Bamboos.
-Crazy.

07:53.150 --> 07:54.760
Crazy, are you deceiving me?

07:54.790 --> 07:56.520
-Well, you...
-Six of Circles.

08:00.180 --> 08:01.310
Nine of Characters.

08:03.270 --> 08:04.120
Sorry.

08:04.150 --> 08:05.410
-Do you win?
-Friends.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.690
Pure Seven Pairs. Nine of Characters.

08:07.690 --> 08:08.760
-Really?
-Oh my god!

08:08.760 --> 08:10.350
That's it. I told you it had to be Brandy.

08:10.350 --> 08:11.740
Well, how did you do that?

08:11.740 --> 08:12.910
Quick, come on!

08:13.720 --> 08:16.820
♪ What was it that brought me to you? ♪

08:17.190 --> 08:19.380
♪ Perhaps it was fate's design ♪

08:17.760 --> 08:18.890
The countdown's on.

08:19.700 --> 08:23.440
♪ Through all our winding paths,
we always find each other ♪

08:21.880 --> 08:25.470
-4, 3, 2, 1!
-4, 3, 2, 1!

08:23.460 --> 08:27.360
♪ The storm turned to rain,
and everything was swept away ♪

08:25.760 --> 08:28.200
Happy New Year!

08:27.380 --> 08:28.660
♪ Slowly, everything becomes clear ♪

08:28.680 --> 08:31.160
♪ In your gaze ♪

08:29.710 --> 08:30.470
Jiang Mu!

08:31.200 --> 08:32.510
Here, here's your red envelope.

08:31.500 --> 08:33.159
♪ I found the answer ♪

08:33.080 --> 08:33.990
Happy New Year to you.

08:33.309 --> 08:35.409
♪ There's a feeling so strong ♪

08:34.960 --> 08:35.990
Thank you, Sanlai.

08:35.429 --> 08:38.580
♪ Our story is still unfolding ♪

08:36.159 --> 08:37.679
For you. Happy New Year,

08:37.830 --> 08:38.510
-Mu.
-Thank you.

08:38.510 --> 08:39.350
I've got more here.

08:38.850 --> 08:43.080
♪ Waiting for the perfect ending ♪

08:39.350 --> 08:40.280
It's from me.

08:40.309 --> 08:41.669
Come on, take it.

08:42.350 --> 08:43.750
Buy yourself something nice to eat.

08:43.750 --> 08:44.870
Thank you all.

08:44.710 --> 08:47.410
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

08:47.440 --> 08:50.000
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

08:47.560 --> 08:48.830
Is this the fireworks show?

08:48.830 --> 08:50.280
Let's go, come on!

08:50.020 --> 08:52.460
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

08:52.490 --> 08:54.090
♪ I just can't help it ♪

08:54.330 --> 08:56.400
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

08:56.800 --> 08:59.280
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

08:58.680 --> 08:59.590
It's beautiful.

08:59.570 --> 09:02.500
♪ Sweet memories ride upon the wind ♪

09:00.230 --> 09:01.090
Happy New Year!

09:01.110 --> 09:03.830
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

09:02.540 --> 09:04.890
♪ I can feel you near ♪

09:04.910 --> 09:07.330
♪ Because I have you by my side ♪

09:07.350 --> 09:10.000
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

09:07.630 --> 09:10.350
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

09:10.020 --> 09:12.120
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

09:10.560 --> 09:11.420
Happy New Year.

09:12.140 --> 09:14.250
♪ We've learned to
cherish each other more ♪

09:14.270 --> 09:16.750
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

09:16.780 --> 09:19.090
♪ The road ahead ♪

09:17.800 --> 09:18.960
Happy New Year!

09:19.080 --> 09:20.400
What did you wish for?

09:19.320 --> 09:21.160
♪ And every step we take ♪

09:21.230 --> 09:23.950
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

09:26.000 --> 09:29.930
♪ We'll both be there ♪

09:45.650 --> 09:46.320
Keys.

09:56.590 --> 09:57.470
Give this to me.

09:57.710 --> 09:59.440
You shouldn't need it anymore.

10:01.200 --> 10:02.230
Oh, so you know about this thing now?

10:02.230 --> 10:03.230
Of course, I know.

10:03.350 --> 10:04.680
I'm right here.

10:04.870 --> 10:07.270
You don't need
to be yearning day and night.

10:12.510 --> 10:14.110
Are you going to take me home?

10:17.680 --> 10:18.680
What do you think?

10:19.870 --> 10:20.560
Okay.

10:21.060 --> 10:22.460
But I have one condition.

10:24.080 --> 10:25.010
What condition?

10:34.630 --> 10:36.360
I want you to carry me upstairs.

10:36.770 --> 10:39.430
Just like what you used to do
when you were young.

10:53.690 --> 10:56.590
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

10:56.980 --> 10:59.950
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

11:00.200 --> 11:02.970
♪ Telling me ♪

11:04.260 --> 11:06.840
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

11:08.860 --> 11:12.090
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

11:12.600 --> 11:15.670
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

11:15.900 --> 11:19.740
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

11:20.130 --> 11:23.780
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

11:24.570 --> 11:27.090
♪ I watch you leave ♪

11:27.900 --> 11:31.340
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

11:31.800 --> 11:34.870
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

11:35.180 --> 11:38.340
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

11:39.930 --> 11:43.090
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

11:43.390 --> 11:46.330
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

11:46.810 --> 11:50.590
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

11:50.610 --> 11:55.300
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

11:54.800 --> 11:55.440
Here we are.

11:55.420 --> 11:58.090
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

11:58.590 --> 12:02.030
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

12:02.770 --> 12:05.040
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

12:05.400 --> 12:08.540
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

12:09.100 --> 12:13.290
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

12:17.800 --> 12:25.140
♪ I'll keep the light on for you ♪

12:21.580 --> 12:22.510
Where is the key?

12:26.280 --> 12:27.070
In my bag.

12:26.620 --> 12:29.840
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

12:30.350 --> 12:33.430
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

12:33.660 --> 12:37.500
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

12:37.890 --> 12:41.540
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

12:42.330 --> 12:44.840
♪ I watch you leave ♪

12:45.660 --> 12:49.090
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

12:49.560 --> 12:52.630
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

12:52.940 --> 12:56.090
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

12:57.690 --> 13:00.840
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

13:01.150 --> 13:04.090
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

13:04.320 --> 13:08.100
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

13:08.130 --> 13:12.570
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

13:12.670 --> 13:15.630
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

13:15.840 --> 13:19.290
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

13:19.960 --> 13:22.240
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

13:22.260 --> 13:25.740
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

13:26.300 --> 13:31.420
♪ This heart that wanders with you ♪

13:31.690 --> 13:35.280
♪ Only wishes you'd smile ♪

13:35.510 --> 13:39.490
♪ All the withered grass on earth ♪

13:39.610 --> 13:44.380
♪ Has bloomed for you ♪

13:47.620 --> 13:50.770
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

13:51.080 --> 13:54.020
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

13:54.490 --> 13:58.280
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

13:58.300 --> 14:02.990
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

14:03.100 --> 14:05.780
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

14:06.170 --> 14:09.620
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

14:10.180 --> 14:12.450
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

14:12.470 --> 14:16.150
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

14:16.540 --> 14:20.740
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

14:25.190 --> 14:32.520
♪ I'll keep the light on for you ♪

15:46.060 --> 15:47.110
Are you leaving?

16:06.040 --> 16:07.170
What else would I do?

16:08.830 --> 16:10.040
When we were little,

16:10.320 --> 16:12.800
we always stayed up
for New Year's Eve together.

16:12.800 --> 16:14.470
You were afraid I couldn't fall asleep,

16:14.470 --> 16:17.130
so you always told me
many interesting stories.

16:18.270 --> 16:20.670
You haven't told me stories
for a long time.

16:26.350 --> 16:27.470
But every time,

16:28.410 --> 16:31.070
you couldn't even stay awake
through one story.

16:31.800 --> 16:34.130
This time I definitely won't fall asleep.

16:48.680 --> 16:50.110
You're not a child anymore.

16:50.110 --> 16:52.110
I'll always be younger than you.

16:56.350 --> 16:57.110
Please?

17:06.829 --> 17:07.790
One hour at most.

17:58.710 --> 17:59.930
I fell asleep by accident.

17:59.930 --> 18:01.750
Where are you? I'll come find you.

18:01.750 --> 18:02.640
Don't rush.

18:03.090 --> 18:04.510
Take your time getting ready.

18:04.510 --> 18:05.840
Have something to eat first.

18:05.840 --> 18:07.500
I'll wait for you downstairs.

18:27.820 --> 18:29.550
How long have you been waiting?

18:34.270 --> 18:35.800
I couldn't reach you by phone.

18:35.800 --> 18:36.860
So I just came over.

18:38.110 --> 18:39.910
Why didn't you come up to wake me?

18:41.600 --> 18:42.660
It was still early.

18:42.710 --> 18:44.770
I wanted to let you sleep a bit longer.

18:46.440 --> 18:47.500
Give me the car key.

18:50.360 --> 18:50.990
What for?

18:51.550 --> 18:52.280
Give it to me.

18:57.350 --> 18:58.420
Let me remind you,

18:58.970 --> 19:00.360
do you even have a driver's license?

19:00.360 --> 19:01.690
-Can you drive?
-Get in.

20:25.230 --> 20:26.510
It's your New Year's gift.

20:26.510 --> 20:27.680
How do you like it?

20:29.030 --> 20:30.160
Who taught you that?

20:30.920 --> 20:31.840
Sanlai said

20:32.030 --> 20:34.290
drifting is the best way to pick up girls.

20:34.640 --> 20:35.440
I was curious,

20:35.440 --> 20:36.550
so I learned it.

20:39.710 --> 20:40.640
You haven't answered me yet.

20:40.640 --> 20:41.840
Do you like it?

20:43.560 --> 20:44.280
I like it.

20:45.380 --> 20:47.640
This is the best gift I've ever received.

20:48.070 --> 20:48.790
Really?

20:49.680 --> 20:50.780
Then I'll go do another drift.

20:50.780 --> 20:51.420
Wait.

20:53.310 --> 20:54.310
Take the passenger seat.

20:54.310 --> 20:55.170
I'll do a drift.

21:40.750 --> 21:42.410
This is my return gift for you.

23:01.640 --> 23:02.270
Brandy!

23:05.640 --> 23:06.310
Sorry.

23:06.710 --> 23:07.910
Sorry, I got stuck in traffic.

23:07.910 --> 23:08.470
Sanlai.

23:08.600 --> 23:09.270
I'm late.

23:09.660 --> 23:11.060
What kind of tree is this?

23:12.640 --> 23:13.510
This one?

23:13.990 --> 23:15.470
This is our wishing tree.

23:15.710 --> 23:16.770
We call it Tree God.

23:17.270 --> 23:18.270
It's very powerful.

23:18.270 --> 23:19.790
Ask for wealth, and you'll get it.

23:19.790 --> 23:21.590
When it comes to asking for love,

23:21.730 --> 23:23.190
it's even more effective.

24:21.510 --> 24:22.230
Jiang Mu,

24:22.670 --> 24:24.250
you need to tell your wish
to the Tree God.

24:24.250 --> 24:25.710
Only then can it bless you.

24:28.880 --> 24:29.940
Tree God, Tree God,

24:30.020 --> 24:31.680
I wish everyone safe and healthy

24:31.680 --> 24:33.270
in the new year.

24:34.020 --> 24:36.220
And please bless Zhao and me...

24:51.870 --> 24:53.750
You've been talking
to the Tree God for so long.

24:53.750 --> 24:55.410
You must have many loved ones.

24:57.040 --> 24:58.770
Don't be ridiculous. Just one.

25:19.880 --> 25:21.330
The lion dance is starting over there.

25:21.330 --> 25:23.590
I heard it's a lion dance team from China.

25:24.070 --> 25:26.130
Let's go. The lion dance is starting.

25:26.570 --> 25:28.230
Lion dance? Let's go, come on.

25:52.000 --> 25:53.400
I forgot this is my zodiac year.

25:53.400 --> 25:54.520
I need to get something red.

25:54.520 --> 25:56.270
You go ahead.
I'll meet you at the parking lot.

25:56.270 --> 25:57.110
See you later.

25:59.580 --> 26:01.310
It's starting. It's starting.

26:03.830 --> 26:04.750
Excuse me.

26:12.040 --> 26:14.390
It's too crowded here. What if I get lost?

26:54.530 --> 26:55.640
You did this for...

27:21.660 --> 27:22.830
I didn't mean to.

27:44.990 --> 27:48.250
I didn't expect the temple fair here
would be quite lively.

27:49.040 --> 27:50.700
I'll bring you here next time.

27:54.330 --> 27:55.330
Brandy?

28:05.020 --> 28:05.690
Let's go.

28:08.630 --> 28:10.030
You're acting like you didn't see us.

28:10.030 --> 28:11.160
Where are you going?

28:11.300 --> 28:12.530
Although we don't work together,

28:12.530 --> 28:14.610
we're not complete strangers, right?

28:14.610 --> 28:15.170
Come on.

28:15.450 --> 28:17.780
Extend your New Year greetings to Mr. Wan.

28:20.910 --> 28:21.590
Follow me.

28:26.940 --> 28:28.000
I'm talking to you.

28:28.920 --> 28:30.550
Extend your New Year greetings to Mr. Wan.

28:30.550 --> 28:31.640
Out of the way.

28:32.460 --> 28:33.260
Out of the way?

28:33.550 --> 28:35.150
Are they getting in your way?

28:35.800 --> 28:36.750
I think you

28:36.750 --> 28:38.480
don't want to leave here alive.

28:42.380 --> 28:43.500
What are you doing?

28:47.240 --> 28:47.900
Move aside.

28:48.250 --> 28:49.380
You have no manners.

28:51.350 --> 28:53.220
Brandy is senior to all of you.

28:53.470 --> 28:55.560
Is this how you were taught to behave?

28:59.160 --> 28:59.890
Brandy.

29:00.090 --> 29:02.370
I was thinking of gathering
some old friends

29:02.370 --> 29:04.600
on the fourth or fifth days
of the lunar New Year.

29:04.600 --> 29:05.800
We're not that close.

29:06.350 --> 29:07.810
Let's skip the gathering.

29:18.070 --> 29:19.530
We don't have to eat together.

29:19.530 --> 29:21.460
But let's be clear about one thing.

29:29.400 --> 29:30.230
I heard

29:30.680 --> 29:33.570
you're planning to interfere
with the business in Xikouguan.

29:33.570 --> 29:35.230
Quite ambitious, aren't you?

29:37.070 --> 29:38.160
Xikouguan?

29:39.530 --> 29:41.550
Whether I interfere or not
isn't up to you.

29:41.550 --> 29:42.880
It's not up to me either.

29:43.070 --> 29:44.250
We'll see who has what it takes.

29:44.250 --> 29:45.600
You're really something,

29:45.600 --> 29:46.870
climbing the ranks ahead of others

29:46.870 --> 29:47.680
and getting so much attention

29:47.680 --> 29:49.270
in such a short time.

29:49.530 --> 29:50.710
Aren't you obviously

29:50.710 --> 29:52.470
going against Mr. Wan?

29:52.880 --> 29:53.760
Let me tell you,

29:54.130 --> 29:55.240
don't be naive.

29:55.260 --> 29:57.060
It's not too late to back off now.

29:57.470 --> 29:58.360
Back off?

29:58.880 --> 29:59.920
What does he mean?

30:00.200 --> 30:02.660
You're so confident
that I'm targeting you?

30:03.500 --> 30:04.830
Why would I go after you?

30:08.710 --> 30:09.880
Alright, alright.

30:10.740 --> 30:12.380
What are you doing?
We're all friends here.

30:12.380 --> 30:14.310
You shouldn't have pointed at him.

30:16.350 --> 30:17.780
Brandy, you don't even know.

30:17.780 --> 30:18.690
Just recently,

30:19.380 --> 30:20.440
Qing argued with me for days

30:20.440 --> 30:21.970
because of your situation.

30:22.700 --> 30:23.460
It seems

30:23.860 --> 30:25.720
my daughter has feelings for you.

30:27.120 --> 30:29.380
I know you're a small business owner now.

30:29.790 --> 30:31.390
Whether big or small business,

30:31.390 --> 30:34.150
business thrives on harmony.

30:34.740 --> 30:36.840
Why lose together
when we can win together,

30:36.840 --> 30:37.430
right?

30:39.360 --> 30:40.320
How do we both win?

30:40.320 --> 30:42.470
I like ambitious young people,

30:42.630 --> 30:43.880
but they

30:43.880 --> 30:44.750
fall into 2 categories for me:

30:44.750 --> 30:47.120
insiders and outsiders.

30:49.720 --> 30:50.960
What difference

30:52.410 --> 30:53.540
does it make?

30:54.800 --> 30:55.670
Brandy.

30:58.350 --> 30:59.980
How well I treat my daughter

31:00.860 --> 31:03.790
is exactly how well I'll treat
my future son-in-law.

31:32.650 --> 31:34.410
But if someone's an outsider,

31:37.750 --> 31:39.410
I can't control what happens.

31:41.410 --> 31:42.480
Can't control it.

32:01.870 --> 32:04.560
What era are we in? Arranged marriages?

32:04.830 --> 32:06.160
How outdated can you be?

32:08.120 --> 32:09.160
Who do we have here?

32:09.160 --> 32:10.990
Shouting through a megaphone.

32:11.170 --> 32:13.650
Turns out it's Lai Qide's son.

32:14.000 --> 32:16.230
I was drinking with your father
before the New Year.

32:16.230 --> 32:18.360
He said you haven't been home for ages.

32:18.440 --> 32:20.710
Next time you have dinner with my dad,

32:20.840 --> 32:22.770
could you remind him of something?

32:22.990 --> 32:24.190
To pay back the money.

32:24.950 --> 32:26.280
That's not my business.

32:26.350 --> 32:28.630
I don't want to get involved
in your father-son issues.

32:28.630 --> 32:30.360
But my friendship with your father

32:30.360 --> 32:31.680
goes way back.

32:31.800 --> 32:32.710
Let me tell you,

32:33.200 --> 32:34.730
you'd better not interfere

32:35.120 --> 32:36.780
with my business with Brandy.

32:36.830 --> 32:39.180
You and my dad go way back.

32:39.550 --> 32:40.550
What a coincidence.

32:40.550 --> 32:42.800
Brandy and I are quite acquainted as well.

32:42.800 --> 32:43.660
I'm definitely

32:43.830 --> 32:45.690
getting involved in this matter.

32:48.970 --> 32:50.090
Come down. Come down.

32:50.090 --> 32:51.820
My neck hurts looking up at you.

32:51.830 --> 32:52.430
Come down.

32:52.710 --> 32:53.770
It's too high here.

32:53.830 --> 32:54.890
I'm afraid to jump.

32:55.630 --> 32:57.360
But if you feel uncomfortable,

32:58.080 --> 32:59.210
you can come up here.

33:00.550 --> 33:02.410
We've arrived at our scenic spot!

33:04.550 --> 33:05.280
Take photos.

33:07.160 --> 33:08.550
Who can take our picture?

33:08.550 --> 33:09.830
Li, of course.

33:11.440 --> 33:12.120
He can do it!

33:12.150 --> 33:13.960
Give me a break.
You know how to take photos?

33:13.960 --> 33:14.640
Get out of here.

33:14.640 --> 33:16.500
Excuse me, we can take your photo!

33:16.600 --> 33:17.930
We're really good at it!

33:17.960 --> 33:19.510
H-He's really good at it.

33:19.540 --> 33:20.200
He can take photos.

33:20.200 --> 33:22.030
I'll join you.

33:22.230 --> 33:23.890
Thank you, young man. Come on.

33:29.550 --> 33:30.740
Dad, forget it.

33:31.640 --> 33:33.870
Alright. Stand still. You look beautiful.

33:33.870 --> 33:34.870
Take a nice photo.

33:35.510 --> 33:36.550
Take more pictures.

33:36.550 --> 33:37.750
Make us look younger.

33:38.400 --> 33:40.860
Young man, come down
and take a photo with us!

33:41.470 --> 33:43.400
Coming! Wait for me. Just a second!

33:44.740 --> 33:46.790
They're leaving. They're leaving.

33:47.040 --> 33:47.970
Coming! Coming!

33:49.870 --> 33:50.870
Coming!

33:50.990 --> 33:53.230
Come on. Let's do this together.

33:54.790 --> 33:55.640
Come here, handsome.

33:55.640 --> 33:57.470
Let's see how your photos turned out,
handsome.

33:57.470 --> 33:59.730
They turned out great. Let's take a look.

34:02.350 --> 34:03.810
I'll head upstairs first.

34:16.440 --> 34:17.239
What's wrong?

34:17.920 --> 34:19.050
Don't want to leave?

34:22.800 --> 34:23.469
No way.

34:24.150 --> 34:24.960
Bye, Sanlai.

34:25.540 --> 34:26.230
Bye.

34:37.630 --> 34:39.360
Don't you think Jiang Mu looks

34:40.770 --> 34:42.630
really pretty dressed like this?

34:46.780 --> 34:48.239
Did you just hold her hand?

34:55.190 --> 34:56.989
I was afraid she'd overthink it.

34:57.510 --> 34:59.040
Afraid she'd overthink it?

35:00.290 --> 35:03.150
Do you even know what she was thinking?
And you worry she would overthink?

35:03.150 --> 35:04.980
Thinking is one thing,
but why did you hold her hand?

35:04.980 --> 35:06.110
Did I hold your hand?

35:07.940 --> 35:09.270
Why are you so worked up?

35:13.300 --> 35:14.610
Brandy, Brandy.

35:15.750 --> 35:17.080
Your karma has arrived.

35:19.800 --> 35:20.840
I told you.

35:20.870 --> 35:22.060
You shouldn't...

35:22.630 --> 35:24.280
Well, you shouldn't always reject women.

35:24.280 --> 35:25.720
I'm telling you, if you reject too many,

35:25.720 --> 35:26.840
when someone you really care about

35:26.840 --> 35:27.470
comes along,

35:27.470 --> 35:29.870
your karma will catch up with you,
you know?

35:46.310 --> 35:47.020
Qing.

35:49.990 --> 35:51.050
What are you doing?

35:54.140 --> 35:54.710
Get lost.

36:02.240 --> 36:03.240
You want to fight?

36:03.790 --> 36:04.350
Fine.

36:04.900 --> 36:05.630
I'm game.

36:49.940 --> 36:50.750
Bear with it.

37:00.040 --> 37:01.040
Does it hurt a lot?

37:49.400 --> 37:50.030
Done.

37:50.310 --> 37:51.570
Let's do the other one.

37:59.610 --> 38:00.870
You can't replace him.

38:45.900 --> 38:47.760
Coming to wish me a happy New Year?

38:47.760 --> 38:48.880
Wan Qing likes you.

38:57.770 --> 39:00.060
If you don't like her,
stay the hell away from her.

39:00.060 --> 39:02.520
Your feelings for Snakey
are your business.

39:03.100 --> 39:04.300
Don't drag me into it.

39:04.350 --> 39:05.550
If it weren't for you,

39:05.930 --> 39:07.730
she wouldn't be so heartbroken.

39:14.810 --> 39:15.850
You're pathetic.

39:29.910 --> 39:30.640
Enough.

39:32.800 --> 39:34.110
I have someone I need to protect.
